videos.headline: Patterson gets loose for 82-yard Buffalo TD
videos.description: Buffalo RB Jaret Patterson powers through the defense and breaks free, scoring from 82 yards out to put the Bulls ahead 14-3.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patterson gets loose for 82-yard Buffalo TD) 2018/09/28

videos.headline: Miami (OH) WR makes acrobatic TD grab
videos.description: Miami (OH) QB Brett Gabbert throws to the end zone and Jalen Walker rises up over the defender to make the catch for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami (OH) WR makes acrobatic TD grab) 2019/09/28
